data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Incredible 3 bed 2.5 bath large living home with 17 x 40 shop!! so many new updates, vinyl windows with magnificent bay window, architectural roof, paint throughout, rich laminate flooring, stainless appliances in the great size kitchen with so much storage and counter space. patios galore for entertaining or enjoying landscaping. deep Double car garage, three car driveway, also a 10 x 85 ft RV parking /storage plus that 17 x 40 ft shop for those hobbies /projects and rec room area, possible duel living too
